Body:
assert type(None) == NULL
assert type('') == NULL
assert type('""') == STRING
assert type('a') == SYMBOL
assert type('"a"') == STRING
assert type('"1"') == STRING
assert type('"escapes \\" and spaces"') == STRING
assert type('1') == INTEGER
assert type('1.5') == FLOAT
assert type('1e-3') == FLOAT
